\lang english
4.
 Compliance and Exceptions
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize

\series bold
\lang english
Mandatory Enforcement
\series default
:
 Personnel who refuse to utilize County-required authentication mechanisms shall be denied access to County information systems.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize

\series bold
\lang english
Sanctions
\series default
:
 Attempting to bypass authentication controls or sharing credentials constitutes a severe security violation subject to disciplinary action up to and including termination and criminal referral under NRS 205.4765.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize

\series bold
\lang english
CJIS Floor
\series default
:
 Exceptions shall not authorize non-compliance with CJIS Security Policy requirements.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize

\series bold
\lang english
Exception Process
\series default
:
 
\end_layout

